div.p: Diagrammatic Summary of the Implementation of the Data-to-Decisions (D2D) Audit and Feedback Program. The figure represents a diagrammatic summary of how interviewed practices implemented the Data-to-Decisions (D2D) audit and feedback program. The observed state of implementation reflected an incomplete feedback loop as characterized by the fact that the response and audit stages were not linked. The feedback stage summarizes the observation that the feedback report was sometimes reformatted prior to review by practice leaders
